  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Building Courses Component**\n\nI\'m now focusing on `/src/components/Courses.tsx`. Initial thoughts revolve around the course display \342\200\223 should I go for a custom horizontal scroll or a grid with a filter? I\'m leaning toward a section header, something like \"Master the Craft. Master the Business.\" to set the stage.\n\n\n**Designing Course Cards**\n\nI\'ve got the course card design sketched out. It\'ll be on a pure white background with a plum border. I\'m prioritizing the image area, which takes up 60% of the card and will feature a placeholder image initially. The content area has padding, with a \"BESTSELLER\" tag, a title (\"The All-in-One Bread Masterclass\"), and the price. On hover, the internal image will scale up, and the border will change to plum. I\'m planning to build a spectacular course catalog list with 4-5 elite courses.\n\n\n**Adding Course Detail Features**\n\nI\'m now thinking about specific course details. I will include a detailed curriculum, duration information, and downloadable resources. I plan a smooth enrollment flow with a \"beautiful checkout\" button. I\'m also looking for high-quality Unsplash images for the course cards.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will create the `/src/components/Courses.tsx` component, introducing an interactive, filterable masterclass directory. This directory includes high-fidelity card animations, hover triggers, detailed syllabus expanders, and a comprehensive curricula modal drawer."
