    thinking: "**Finalizing Verification**\n\nI\'m now in the process of finalizing and verifying the complete state, as requested. Everything appears to have been built successfully. I\'m reviewing the initial requests to ensure all tasks are complete before finalizing the state.\n\n\n**Defining Component Structure**\n\nI have successfully defined the component structure. I\'ve finished the transparent minimal navigation, dual-action cinematic hero, and social proof marquee, forward and backward. I am working on the interactive elements.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed the production-ready build for **Mumma\342\200\231s Cake**, transforming the digital storefront for Mahek Baldota into an elite, boutique editorial experience that beautifully bridges her Culinary Academy and local luxury bakery.\n\nThe application successfully builds and passes all TypeScript/Linter validations. Here is an overview of the aesthetic and functional implementation:\n\n### \342\234\246 Editorial Art Direction & Token Architecture\n*   **Washed Alabaster Canvas (`#F9F8F6`)**: Executed an exclusive premium light theme, completely banning generic dark UI or SaaS blue templates in favor of physical magazine aesthetics.\n*   **The Signature Plum Contrast (`#211426`)**: All text, primary elements, and core accents utilize a heavy premium purple-black shade, offset by muted, dust-brushed **Mauve (`#A68A9A`)** accents.\n*   **High-Contrast Typographic Pairings**: Anchored the brand by importing **Instrument Serif** for massive, tightly spaced display headings (`leading-[0.9]`), paired alongside **Inter** for clean, brutalist geometric labels.\n\n---\n\n### \342\234\246 Creative Component Blueprint\n*   **Component A (Minimalist Header Navigation)**: A fixed glass landing bar with blur transitions (`backdrop-blur-md bg-cream/85`) when scrolling. Features sitemap hotlinks and a high-contrast learn button.\n*   **Component B (Dual-Action Cinematic Hero)**: Configured as an asymmetrical split. \n    *   *Left*: Features a staggered line reveal of the central H1 statement using premium cubic-bezier easing curves, paired with customized active action tags.\n    *   *Right*: Highlights the viral chocolate fudge bowl masked inside a tall architectural masonry arch (`rounded-t-full`) with an automatic slow-scale zoom animation and high-end hovering badge details.\n*   **Component C (Infinite Social Proof Marquees)**: Interactive double-row horizontal moving tracks separator styled on deep plum backgrounds containing star asterisks.\n*   **Component D (Prestige Masterclasses Grid)**: Interlocks beautiful course materials with individual categories, price quotes, star feedback ratings, and custom hover states that smoothly expand internal assets. Click-through displays trigger a detailed syllabus drawer containing a real-time mock enrollment confirmation flow.\n*   **Component E (Bespoke Bakery Configurator)**: A beautiful step-by-step custom weight, flavor profiling, and heavy-textured decoration styling interface. Submitting logs creates a customized printable order ticket receipt with real-time price estimation.\n*   **Component F (The Founder\'s Kitchen)**: A high-contrast historical storyteller section for Mahek Baldota\'s 85K+ follower journey, complete with verified graduate testimonial sliders and unified query accordion desks."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 3
      nanos: 82825087
