    thinking: "**Considering Cake Strategy**\n\nI\'m wrestling with the removal of the bakery menu while still highlighting Mahek\'s cake expertise. Currently, I\'m leaning toward prominent, visually-driven cake features and links to her teaching platform. The goal is to retain the cake business\'s \"shout\" while streamlining the website.\n\n\n**Pivoting to the Academy**\n\nNow I\'m completely shifting to \"The Academy,\" and building six-figure cake businesses. Mahek\'s viral cakes will be used as undeniable proof of work. I\'m focusing on \"The Cake Artistry Gallery\" showcasing her masterpieces, with details on her design, textures, and methods. I also have an idea for a dynamic \"Cake Crumb & Texture Analyzer\", a visual sandbox to illustrate perfect crumb structures and temperature heat maps to highlight her \"Science-First Formulas\". I want the frontend to be \"poppy and vibrant, but not too much\".\n\n\n**Designing the Interactive Component**\n\nI\'m now integrating a \"Baking Profit Calculator\" as a key interactive element. I envision a sleek design, allowing users to manipulate variables like order volume, costs, and markups. This will demonstrate the earning potential of baking businesses, ideally driving sales to the \"Ultimate Cake Business Blueprint\" masterclass. Simultaneously, I\'m working on the design aspects, aiming for a poppy but premium aesthetic with color accents like glazed vanilla cream, velvet maroon, and elegant gold. I have a list of files to update.\n\n\n**Updating the Interactive Sandbox**\n\nI\'m now implementing the interactive texture sandbox, focusing on user interaction with \"Crumb Varieties.\" I\'m also planning to incorporate elegant visualizations as users click to view various cake crumb examples. My focus is on making this a standout feature in the new \"Cake Artistry Lab,\" replacing the bakery menu. I am working on the front-end now.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 6
      nanos: 187317759
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
