    thinking: "**Crafting Component Architecture**\n\nI\'m now diving into the component architecture, focusing on `/src/components/CakeArtistryLab.tsx`. My current focus is structuring it with two distinct sections: a \"Visual Masterpieces Gallery\" showcasing Mahek\'s textured cakes, highlighting the \"Texture Challenge\" and \"Formula Secret\" for each. Let\'s make this an absolute masterpiece of a component!\n\n\n**Developing Interactive Lab**\n\nI\'ve transitioned to the \"Interactive Lab\" section, focusing on two key features. First, the \"Interactive Crumb & Chemistry Simulator\" will allow students to click on baking anomalies and visualize them with simulated cake cross-sections and temperature curves. Secondly, the \"Bespoke Profit Calculator\" is designed for home bakers to model profit based on sales and pricing. The art direction will be implemented, creating a luxurious editorial feel with vibrant raspberry maroon, honey glazed yellow, deep plum, warm cream, and velvet accents.\n\n\n"
