  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Celebrating Build Success**\n\nEverything compiled without a hitch! I\'m really pleased with the outcome. Now, I\'m shifting focus to summarizing the achievements. My goal is to follow our communication guidelines, ensuring clarity and professionalism in the explanation. I\'m aiming for a simple, conversational style, avoiding jargon.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed your request to refocus the website from retail cake sales to a highly captivating, premium, and interactive course-selling experience that **shouts about the art of cakes**. \n\nHere is an overview of the premium design and functional elements implemented:\n\n### \342\234\246 Visual Identity & Refined Palette\n*   **The Raspberry Velvet Aesthetic**: Infused tasteful touches of vibrant raspberry maroon (`#80173F`) and warm honey glass yellow (`#FFFEEF`) to drop the static minimalist look and introduce poppy, high-density colors.\n*   **No Generic Emojis**: Removed all emoji placeholders and replaced them with crisp, professional micro-vector iconography matching the luxury editorial magazine identity.\n\n---\n\n### \342\234\246 High-Contrast Frontend Features\n\n#### 1. The Cake Artistry Showcase (Proof-of-Work)\nInstead of a simple booking form, we now emphasize Mahek\'s actual viral masterpieces to seal her credential authority:\n*   **Interactive Exhibition**: Users can toggle between her actual viral specimen recipes (such as the *Impasto Palette-Knife Bloom* or *Gilded Architectural Concrete*) to immediately reveal the **Structural Texture Ratings**, verified **Viral Reels Metrics**, and detailed **Molecular Chemistry Secrets**.\n\n#### 2. The Molecular Pastry Lab (Interactive Simulation)\nBaking isn\'t a game of guessing; it\'s physics. This interactive widget invites students to inspect crumb structures at a cellular level:\n*   **Microstructure Simulation**: Clicking through crumb states (such as the *Sunk Wet Center* or *Coarse Brittle Crumb*) dynamically alters a clean cellular canvas with scientific diagnoses of gluten coagulations, chemical failures, and the exact academy-proven formulaic fix.\n\n#### 3. Bespoke Profit Calculator (Business Estimator)\nTo convert aspiring home-bakers into students, we built a beautiful slider calculator:\n*   **Pricing Leverage Ledger**: Users can slide cakes baked per week, custom artwork retail prices, and material budgets to see monthly profit forecasts in real-time.\n*   **Branding Power Insight**: Dynamically calculates and teaches how changing brand perception from a simple kitchen hobbyist to a premium culinary architect elevates their margin potential by over **280%** on the exact same ingredient budget."
    thinking_duration {
      nanos: 727224252
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
