    thinking: "**Eliminating Unwanted Components**\n\nI\'ve just removed `CakeArtistryLab.tsx`, and am now working through the codebase to eliminate all related references. Specifically, I\'m checking `Navigation.tsx`, `Hero.tsx`, and `App.tsx` for any lingering dependencies or imports. I\'m making sure to clean up the code efficiently.\n\n\n**Reframing the Cake Artistry**\n\nI\'m now completely restructuring the \"Cake Artistry Lab\" concept. Instead of a simulation or calculator, I\'m pivoting towards a visually arresting \"Cake Artistry Showcase.\" I\'m planning a static, highly visual component called `CakeArtistryShowcase.tsx`. This aims to highlight Mahek\'s cake designs through stunning photography, editorial layouts, and storytelling focused on texture and artistry. It will replace the removed lab component.\n\n\n**Designing the Showcase Content**\n\nI\'m now deep diving into the content strategy for the showcase. I\'m focusing on beautiful, high-quality visuals of cakes and pastries, paired with clean typography and elegant narrative panels describing the design processes. I\'m leaning toward an interactive slider or tab system for a high-contrast experience, avoiding simulations entirely. I\'ll focus on making this component show Mahek\'s artistry through design and text!\n\n\n"
