    web_documents {
      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGcBz7UdKbKBCJ15AubSyC8vqIH8-ZravcY8ZZc5qHRSk7lhWm0YQjA5oAIuJl-cJkYqkiViW9LhPmYe3cq0V1A7eOpXtu9EER6o2MZWnCHl2umGbExJC-93KhXk5kNtYyGKLJBMb7mLKud_qGuAIn0lDSMCHshcjoNUg28QwLbQNQqcUde3NgKDyZVczHMQqkWckfJxItN7iXBze88CWgmZkY6I7n60FB9NUjFtBExmS46"
      title: "stackoverflow.com"
    }
    summary: "The error message \"Cannot set property fetch of #<Window> which has only a getter\" indicates that there is an attempt to modify the `fetch` property directly on the `window` object in a web browser environment. This action is not allowed because `window.fetch` is a built-in, read-only property that functions as a getter, meaning it can only return a value and cannot be reassigned or redefined[1][2][3][4].\n\nThe `fetch()` method is a standard Web API that allows web browsers to make network requests, returning a Promise that resolves to a `Response` object[2][5]. Since it\'s an intrinsic part of the browser\'s `Window` interface, its implementation is controlled by the browser, and direct modification is prevented to maintain stability and security[2][6][5].\n\nThis error typically arises in situations such as:\n*   **Incorrect Polyfilling:** When a developer attempts to provide a polyfill for the `fetch` API in an environment where `window.fetch` already natively exists. The polyfill might try to overwrite the existing, non-writable property, leading to this error.\n*   **Third-Party Libraries or Scripts:** A library or script might be trying to manipulate or replace the global `fetch` function for various reasons (e.g., for mocking, interception, or custom behavior) without properly checking if it\'s writable[1].\n*   **Strict Mode:** Code executing in JavaScript\'s strict mode can be more aggressive in enforcing immutability and will throw an error if an attempt is made to write to a read-only property[7][4].\n\nTo resolve this error, the code attempting to set the `window.fetch` property needs to be identified and revised. Instead of directly assigning a new value to `window.fetch`, alternative approaches should be considered, such as:\n*   **Conditional Polyfilling:** Only apply a polyfill if `window.fetch` does not already exist.\n*   **Wrapping or Intercepting:** If custom behavior is required, consider wrapping the native `fetch` function within another function and then calling the original `fetch` inside the wrapper, rather than overwriting `window.fetch` itself.\n\nSources:\n[1] [google.dev](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGjArj7s28sZymPwiz2iEIG8EWMpDq5PSzgyU8ITCjiZQ4jjrG0tQL4x5FLQK0xI89J4EyDzoFR4m2Rt5jqGTOTg-ljelmZOXQU1mrEJvTKH4NaH1RycQpcKKCY52Q6qG1mjKjNmxwEXSbBJd4ImoWdKYgCqv3dUKML3eJvz_iATK79_yVu_Cii7DJMEz-O2vCUE3m9zqaxWzcpZxJuiBETqsfT5D8jFIG8W5wLKhXlgw==)\n[2] [mozilla.org](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJS8wKoOfmkpnC2JWnhMFxoN4NkZUNeyhYd9dpfZjANFeLmlrHIXzA5Jd7gGF2258vEEC2olSzkMjeAAnn-cWS4r3utke4Qbtt5-wFVD9Biqm0kKA3Hpqqj6rc62pU-3e8ClC1atIFplyrhUlaMl3Y75ldRJ4qCBA=)\n[3] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEIJivywF6p69LA_XF0LfyByIesWc6E9bx3NDiRiD75L13TRoEoNGP1pQKBoMB5y1XntvhM9qx3U9DYXb2NE9QhODYsQFbdAXe4DfbO4Yg_hm5J9Tnspk0yWi8P3NPnGO9zJT2cDo8rDSL_X-6ipRph_U5ytJ0H8nCvOFqv7oPQbN4ZALvYXcdqFDaIw3lQ5jl_3T9wRp09cxuPhHB7wQcq)\n[4] [zipy.ai](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFlg4H9a2C_O95V_mqfCDzVGiFsf5oRl3CbagrvIRrwM_Glp3xKs7ZcQIQd3phWsQuTMjJ1MukgPAHZnhzISoZ4cHLCUs19GHeKbCHGOmTsI13YYp7hM6bq3n6VOTXtLC_pg8sQyvfYDpUbN4WycmOzMBWiYvBDaxVcEXO-EbMSXg==)\n[5] [reddit.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFuAhZftxtovJBlOn_PS_rNghpL-StkruLsorHcw5XHtmd3T5xjM12zPBEwsmPg1mYZ2mq9d9o_17V-I0RHUOdxdOc3Q3HEoj8LJkPt4yPHHXtY-D3mE1sBcQWihfQ6sJSr-3Wf4rDDBMr-hSUTnR6Yz4RbHC7StYD61BizC04dQOQIKSD191YKSphYIXoLStYLyA==)\n[6] [whatwg.org](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQENME1QaRrMdkT5L2lsTz92Bfarf0F4fQs2nLGFbw1Kw20uVfE36dtOSRwj7RzAzzo5NTB9zvxuCfSygRyl-5lPre_uOwbJ8P3Rh3WXNnmYxXzaqsp91QPEhA==)\n[7] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGcBz7UdKbKBCJ15AubSyC8vqIH8-ZravcY8ZZc5qHRSk7lhWm0YQjA5oAIuJl-cJkYqkiViW9LhPmYe3cq0V1A7eOpXtu9EER6o2MZWnCHl2umGbExJC-93Kh