          text: "### [current community](https://stackoverflow.com)\n[current community](https://stackoverflow.com)\n- \n\n                [Stack Overflow](https://stackoverflow.com)\n\n\n\n            [help](https://stackoverflow.com/help)\n            [chat](https://chat.stackoverflow.com/?tab=explore)\n\n\n\n- \n\n\n\n\n                            [Meta Stack Overflow](https://meta.stackoverflow.com)\n\n\n[Stack Overflow](https://stackoverflow.com)\n[help](https://stackoverflow.com/help)\n[chat](https://chat.stackoverflow.com/?tab=explore)\n[Meta Stack Overflow](https://meta.stackoverflow.com)\n\n### your communities\n[Sign up](https://stackoverflow.com/users/signup?ssrc=site_switcher&returnurl=https%3a%2f%2fstackoverflow.com%2fquestions%2f69055811%2fr-how-to-modify-a-createtable-function-for-reiterated-observations-and-with-t)\n[log in](https://stackoverflow.com/users/login?ssrc=site_switcher&returnurl=https%3a%2f%2fstackoverflow.com%2fquestions%2f69055811%2fr-how-to-modify-a-createtable-function-for-reiterated-observations-and-with-t)"
