          text: "### Sign up or [log in](https://stackoverflow.com/users/login?ssrc=question_page&returnurl=https%3a%2f%2fstackoverflow.com%2fquestions%2f69055811%2fr-how-to-modify-a-createtable-function-for-reiterated-observations-and-with-t%23new-answer)\n[log in](https://stackoverflow.com/users/login?ssrc=question_page&returnurl=https%3a%2f%2fstackoverflow.com%2fquestions%2f69055811%2fr-how-to-modify-a-createtable-function-for-reiterated-observations-and-with-t%23new-answer)\n\n### Post as a guest\nRequired, but never shown\nBy clicking \342\200\234Post Your Answer\342\200\235, you agree to our [terms of service](https://stackoverflow.com/legal/terms-of-service/public) and acknowledge you have read our [privacy policy](https://stackoverflow.com/legal/privacy-policy).\nStart asking to get answers\nFind the answer to your question by asking.\n[Ask question](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/ask)\nExplore related questions\n- [r](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/r)\n- [create-table](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/create-table)\n- [median](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/median)\n- [qq](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/qq)\n[r](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/r)\n[create-table](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/create-table)\n[median](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/median)\n[qq](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/qq)\nSee similar questions with these tags.\n[R Language\n                        Collective\n\n\n                    See more](https://stackoverflow.com/collectives/r-language)\n[This question is in a collective:](https://stackoverflow.com/collectives)\n- \n                            The Overflow Blog\n\n- \n\n\n\n                [You don\342\200\231t understand DNS like you think you...](https://stackoverflow.blog/2026/06/19/you-don-t-understand-dns-like-you-think-you-do/)\n\n\n- \n\n\n\n                [Dispatches from O\'Reilly: From capabilities to...](https://stackove