      title: "github.com"
    }
    summary: "The error message \"Cannot set property fetch of\" typically indicates a `TypeError` in JavaScript. This error occurs when you try to assign a value to a property on an object that is `undefined` or `null`.[1][2][3] In simpler terms, you\'re attempting to modify a property on something that doesn\'t exist or hasn\'t been properly initialized.[1]\n\n**Common Causes:**\n\n1.  **Uninitialized Object:** The most frequent cause is trying to set a property on a variable that has been declared but not assigned an object value. Therefore, the variable\'s value is `undefined`.[1][3][4]\n    *   *Example:*\n        \n\nSources:\n[1] [medium.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHrb6-eejcuzkWoIUEF-r3qXrsKkGzOg_TY-4jZSqylxTIbSqkw5PEkVqCSzqRaQs0zBpvoEyvMdzFP-W4KZaih_QxCATwuyYyDzlQld97Odh8kdmsaK5C3BqaqUMO-ZbqlsaokWaZTvl-BcRy3pQLYbL74y52g2vhEMaHTif3wVqJ8GiEAteHUwKc4H9594f44iiuB7Y4E7G-GrGesqs9QOZXKOz5JP6XPDSncGZE5vw==)\n[2] [kinsta.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEttFO43_pL_VpKiAhN5B03k8RTmX62MAA3xzRq72Sq-uGPLhftBe6CAdHlNp6sIsugEmrHo9sO32neuAPkBG9x1OgXxEkXGDwv93eoe-CTAQkrqCP834QnT5XBLsHduAaO7CijkQMVF5yWLUSlhBKXnwY79bX3sbJFuw==)\n[3] [geeksforgeeks.org](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFAUsPl5bmWYnoSW92PkuJ91a7WLrNU8lSaSYk2z-D-hOKJf02vcswN3JrH3VSY8pmDA9ZU8Rivx_qoREQCjcSnqBM8oHxTzhLqKpPglp-mp3_ZfLHBe8aK9227nKXrhoQijERD4Tte6R8m4OOrRAZ9BDiaC6p-lAIOVBXkJdtVwT09o4bXkKgjOH9bOmPlOTf8_0x9ARxJN2ttMBA2DUDmd25PSOtuzw==)\n[4] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGR4ynfcKOhJVyo4mijuRuwsoc_ohIqMu7RvIv_qHijQ3z8-emT8tsAKMwFFdNM-Uy5N86xVXFJnL4Mp_rzi8_1O82_fNIt_4voIY8dmy3Or9mfySmVTwMizNvnyRSTtLtaGssvPo9GxZh_hCdAvL_35YFPk7hPNr3Loiob4n-HRc33EQY1G5pUXFQmrMpGvvr1Pw==)\n[5] [youtube.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGaNxY9v-AJvjIWlahdxhM3CBsyLKdL9hiHoRY2uccdTkVh645-t4QL7x0c1QXvmE57LaFZlW-A